    "Therefore, experimental procedures to improve the quality of nucleic acids from FFPE samples and minimize false positives must be optimized.",
    "Experimental approaches have been suggested to minimize FFPE-induced artifacts.",
    "Uracil-DNA glycosylase (UDG) and thymine-DNA glycosylase remove deoxyuridine from dU:G mismatch and thymine from T:G mismatch, respectively, consequently generating abasic sites 7, 8.",
